                        <li class="program-details"><i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i> Scandura oblica</li>
                        <li class="program-details"><i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i> Scandura cu atingere laterala</li>
                        <li class="program-details"><i class="fa fa-check" aria-hidden="true"></i> Scaunul roman</li>
